CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 26, 1955, pg. 5 reads: "Boys Clubs Exhibit - William S. Howell, director of Kay Boys Club; Maurice Cohill, Kay Club board member, and Adam N. Miller of Pittsburgh Boys Club, are shown as they inspected the Boys Clubs of America exhibits now on display at Kaufmann's Dining Room on the eleventh floor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: William S. Howell, Maurice Cohill, and Adam N. Miller, standing in front of Kay Boys' Club display in Kaufmann's Dining Room
